column5: I'm looking for a good walleye lakes that isn't far from 502 or Dryden. Any suggestions?
I have fished Cozy camp on the english river, been great for us, Dan the camp owner is a great guy will get you on fish.
Eagle, off 502, not far from Dryden.
Rainy Lake would be a great option and is a great walleye fishery.
Will, Wabigoon is right there. Take a look. PjShorthorn.
